HTML-Perlinfo version 1.61
=========================

NAME
HTML::Perlinfo - Display a lot of Perl information in HTML format

DESCRIPTION
This module outputs a large amount of information about your Perl 
installation in HTML. So far, this includes information about 
Perl compilation options, the Perl version, server information
 and environment, HTTP headers, OS version information, 
Perl modules, and more.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None


